en_160401_0	4 women walking along the shores off the Chilaw coastline, were swept away by a strong current last evening.
en_160401_1	It has been reported that they were taking photographs with their backs to the sea shore.
en_160401_2	The four were abruptly swept away, 3 of them were rescued.
en_160401_3	However a 21 year old is still reported missing.
en_160401_4	The women are residents of Chilaw- Ilippadeniya.
en_160401_5	Police and Navy officers from Kalpitiya have commenced search operations to locate the missing woman.
